title: Error on items or?
body:
These items are showing up, with no picture/never heard of them. Are they there for the next patch or put in the game too early?
[IMG]http://i65.tinypic.com/24lspxc.png[/IMG]

replies.body: They're items for the upcoming new gamemode Nexus Siege. I didn't think the new gamemode was going to be a this patch thing though, so either they were pushed into live early for one reason or another or we'll be seeing Nexus Siege this patch.
